---
// Visualizes the shift from keyword search to natural-language AI prompts:
// the same person types a few keywords into Google but describes a whole
// situation to AI — and only a few words point at the brand/category.
---
<div class="qc">
  <div class="qc__side">
    <span class="qc__tag">the old way · Google</span>
    <div class="qc__bar qc__bar--g">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="qc__icon"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="16" y1="16" x2="21" y2="21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      <span>running shoes for knee pain</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="qc__side">
    <span class="qc__tag">how they actually search now · AI</span>
    <div class="qc__bar qc__bar--ai">
      <p class="qc__prompt">
        ok so i keep getting <mark>knee pain</mark> after my runs and i just signed up for my first
        <mark>half marathon</mark> in the fall, mostly training on <mark>pavement</mark> — what <mark>running shoes</mark>
        actually won’t wreck my joints? budget’s flexible if they last.
      </p>
      <span class="qc__send" aria-hidden="true">➤</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="qc__cap">
    Nobody types keywords into AI. They describe a whole situation — and only a few
    words point at your category. That’s why a keyword tool misses it, and why the
    audit listens for the <em>situations</em> your buyers describe, not the terms they type.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .qc { display: grid; gap: var(--space-3); max-width: 760px; }
  .qc__tag { display: inline-block; font-family: var(--font-sub); font-weight: 800; font-style: italic; color: var(--olive); font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-1); }
  .qc__bar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-2);
    background: var(--cream); border: 2px solid var(--brown);
    border-radius: 999px; padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-3);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }
  .qc__bar--g { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .qc__bar--g span { color: var(--brown); }
  .qc__icon { width: 1.2rem; height: 1.2rem; flex: none; }
  .qc__bar--ai { border-radius: 20px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .qc__prompt { margin: 0; flex: 1; line-height: 1.55; }
  .qc__prompt mark { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--amber) 55%, var(--cream)); color: var(--brown); padding: 0 0.15em; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; }
  .qc__send {
    flex: none; display: grid; place-items: center; width: 2rem; height: 2rem;
    border-radius: 50%; background: var(--rust); color: var(--cream); font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .qc__cap { font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 60ch; margin: 0; }
</style>
